[crickets chirping]

44:46.161 --> 44:47.641
[growling]

44:48.816 --> 44:51.514
Oh, Jesus...

44:51.558 --> 44:53.691
Oh, no...

44:55.736 --> 44:58.434
Oh, God, not again.

45:00.959 --> 45:02.221
[sighs]

45:02.264 --> 45:06.268
Daryl, you poor
son of a bitch.

45:11.186 --> 45:13.711
♪♪

45:31.772 --> 45:33.600
[paper rustling]

46:07.286 --> 46:08.766
- [drawer closing]
- Fuck.

46:09.854 --> 46:12.334
♪♪

46:27.349 --> 46:29.612
You fuckin' bastard.

46:46.760 --> 46:48.240
[growling]

46:51.896 --> 46:53.636
What the fuck?

46:56.422 --> 46:58.728
[frustrated] Shit!

46:58.772 --> 47:00.948
Okay, okay.

47:00.992 --> 47:03.777
Are you okay?
[sighs]

47:03.821 --> 47:05.779
Deep breaths, okay?
Deep breaths.

47:05.823 --> 47:06.824
All right,come on.

47:07.825 --> 47:09.043
Come on, let's go!

47:10.740 --> 47:12.742
[Juliet exhales sharply]

47:12.786 --> 47:14.222
- Hey.
- What?

47:20.620 --> 47:23.101
♪♪

47:26.844 --> 47:28.802
We need to get
to the cop car
quickly. Come on.

47:32.371 --> 47:34.895
♪♪

47:53.914 --> 47:55.785
Hey! Shit.

47:57.004 --> 47:58.571
Jesus Christ!

48:00.225 --> 48:01.879
- What the hell are you
doing out here?
- Shh!

48:01.922 --> 48:04.751
There's--there's somethingout there.

48:04.794 --> 48:07.058
And I-- I saw--

48:07.101 --> 48:10.278
I saw it eat that man,I tried to help him, but...

48:10.322 --> 48:13.281
- You saw what?
- I saw it eat
that man.

48:13.325 --> 48:16.632
- [Lisa breathing hard]
- Okay.

48:16.676 --> 48:20.419
Look, Miss,
I'm gonna need you
to come on with me.

48:20.462 --> 48:23.770
No, no, no,I don't wanna move.What if it comes back?

48:23.813 --> 48:26.512
Well, if that thing
comes back, I'll shoot it.

48:26.555 --> 48:29.123
- Okay?
- How do you know
it will work?

48:29.167 --> 48:32.083
I mean, how do you knowbullets can hurt it?

48:32.126 --> 48:33.998
Ma'am, all I know is,

48:34.041 --> 48:37.523
we can't stay here
under this damn tree.

48:37.566 --> 48:41.744
Come on, I'm gonna get
to my car and I'm gonna
call for backup.

48:41.788 --> 48:42.920
Okay?

48:43.964 --> 48:45.400
Come on!

48:47.925 --> 48:50.928
This is certainlynot usable anymore.

48:50.971 --> 48:53.147
All right.
Take it easy.

48:54.583 --> 48:55.671
Stop right there!

48:55.715 --> 48:57.543
- Juliet! Wendy!
- Lisa!

48:59.371 --> 49:00.850
What did you do
to my radio?

49:00.894 --> 49:02.243
I'm not doinganything with your radio.

49:02.287 --> 49:04.289
I-I came out hereto see if I could make a call

49:04.332 --> 49:07.205
- and I found it like this.
- Why didn't you use
a telephone?

49:07.248 --> 49:10.338
- We don't have any
set up yet.
- Cell phone.

49:11.731 --> 49:13.298
Look, Sheriff...

49:13.341 --> 49:15.735
the-the tireson that truck are slashed.

49:15.778 --> 49:17.955
I-I don't knowwhat is going on out here.

49:17.998 --> 49:21.436
What truck? I thought
you said you were
alone out here.

49:21.480 --> 49:25.005
I... yeah. Right.

49:25.049 --> 49:28.487
- They had my sister and I...
- Okay, all right,
all right.

49:31.664 --> 49:34.449
These boys... these boys
are gonna be the death of me.

49:36.016 --> 49:36.974
Okay.

49:38.888 --> 49:41.543
[exhales sharply]
Now, where are they?

49:41.587 --> 49:43.110
They're in the house.

49:47.462 --> 49:49.116
- Well...
- Good evening, Sheriff.

49:51.075 --> 49:53.860
You boys done
playing house?

49:53.903 --> 49:55.818
Maybe.

49:55.862 --> 49:59.779
- Yeah, we were just--
- Shut the fuck up, Billy!

49:59.822 --> 50:03.304
- You gave these girls
quite the scare.
- "Quite the scare"?

50:03.348 --> 50:06.568
They locked usin a closet and wererobbing the place.

50:06.612 --> 50:09.310
What are you waiting for?
A-arrest them!

50:09.354 --> 50:11.660
Hang on, now, I wanna get
to the bottom of this.

50:11.704 --> 50:14.402
What the hell
are you people doing?

50:14.446 --> 50:16.317
Mm?

50:16.361 --> 50:17.666
I had enough of your shit.

50:17.710 --> 50:20.452
Why do you insist
on fuckin' around?

50:20.495 --> 50:23.542
No, we're...
staying out of trouble.

50:23.585 --> 50:25.065
- Trouble?
- Yeah.

50:25.109 --> 50:26.762
Look, what Billy
is trying to say--

50:26.806 --> 50:28.938
The last thing we need
around here is you.

50:28.982 --> 50:31.637
- Oh, yeah?
- Yeah, we're just
looking for Daryl

50:31.680 --> 50:33.813
- and we're gonna
be leaving.
- Looking for Daryl, huh?

50:33.856 --> 50:36.946
- That's the plan.
- You better change
that plan.

50:36.990 --> 50:39.471
- Is that right?
- I found Daryl.

50:39.514 --> 50:41.473
- Oh, yeah?
- Dead.

50:41.516 --> 50:43.214
In the orchard,
over there.

50:43.257 --> 50:45.651
- I'm sorry, what?
- That's right.

50:45.694 --> 50:47.696
I found that fat
son of a bitch

50:47.740 --> 50:51.048
under the tree
in that orchard out there.

50:51.091 --> 50:53.267
Same place I'd found
that other son of a bitch

50:53.311 --> 50:54.399
a couple of months ago.

50:55.965 --> 50:59.534
Now, I can't keep cleaning up
after you guys,

50:59.578 --> 51:02.233
- blood or no blood.
- Yeah, no one ever
asked you to, Dad.

51:03.930 --> 51:06.759
- Wait, you're related to...
- To all of them, ma'am.

51:08.108 --> 51:09.631
These boys have been
a pain in my ass

51:09.675 --> 51:13.026
ever since the day
each one of them was born.

51:13.070 --> 51:16.029
But they're still my boys.

51:16.073 --> 51:18.510
- Wendy! Wendy...
- Wait!

51:18.553 --> 51:20.033
- God dammit!
- [grunts]

51:20.077 --> 51:22.601
- What the hell's wrong
with you?
- Dad!

51:22.644 --> 51:25.691
You'd think that you
of all fuckin' people

51:25.734 --> 51:29.086
would be a little more
appreciative of the bullshit
I have to put up with

51:29.129 --> 51:33.002
- to keep your ass out of jail!- What's he talking about,Billy?

51:33.046 --> 51:35.657
Now, if it's all right
with you pinheads,

51:35.701 --> 51:39.966
I'd like to clean up
this mess before it gets
any worse.

51:40.009 --> 51:42.142
[Lenny] Want me to go
after the other one?

51:42.186 --> 51:45.972
No. I think whatever'sout there will probablytake care of her...

51:47.365 --> 51:50.629
you... and you.

51:50.672 --> 51:53.719
All right. Hey, hey,
why don't we just
calm down a little bit?

51:53.762 --> 51:56.069
- Right? You don't have
to do this.
- What?

51:56.113 --> 51:57.984
- He's soft for that one.
- Wait.

51:59.942 --> 52:01.118
That one.

52:04.164 --> 52:07.341
All right.
I won't shoot them.

52:07.385 --> 52:10.736
Yet. Take them
in the house.

52:10.779 --> 52:12.825
- I'm not doing that.
- Go.

52:12.868 --> 52:14.609
Go on!

52:14.653 --> 52:16.698
Billy, you don't
have to do this.

52:16.742 --> 52:18.787
- [girls gasp]
- [Wendy] No!

52:24.576 --> 52:28.014
If he's soft on that one,
I'd hate to see
when he was mad.

52:30.408 --> 52:32.366
How much gas
you got in that truck?

52:32.410 --> 52:34.063
What? Why?Where are we going?

52:36.283 --> 52:41.114
[emphatic] How much gas
do you have in that truck?

52:42.811 --> 52:45.292
♪♪

53:01.526 --> 53:03.832
[breathing hard]

53:09.577 --> 53:12.101
♪♪

53:37.997 --> 53:39.651
Hey. How was your shower?

53:39.694 --> 53:42.741
It was delightful.
Wish you would've
joined me.

53:42.784 --> 53:44.656
Yeah, and we would've
never got out of here.

53:44.699 --> 53:46.092
[chuckles]

53:46.135 --> 53:48.573
Hmm. No, really.

53:48.616 --> 53:51.010
I really wish
you would've joined me.

53:51.053 --> 53:53.099
Oh...

53:53.142 --> 53:56.798
- Mm. [chuckles]
- Oh! Wow!

53:56.842 --> 54:00.411
- What would I do
without you?
- [laughs]

54:00.454 --> 54:01.890
- How are you feeling?
- Better.

54:01.934 --> 54:04.153
Wow. Good, yeah.
I feel really good now.

54:04.197 --> 54:07.069
[laughs]
How are you feeling?

54:07.113 --> 54:10.377
Good. I can't stop
thinking about the girls,
but I feel good.

54:10.421 --> 54:12.771
I can't either. Maybe
this is the last time we...

54:14.425 --> 54:16.035
Maybe this is the last time
we travel without them.

54:17.602 --> 54:19.299
- I know it is.
- Oh!

54:19.343 --> 54:21.258
- A mother would know.
- Yeah.

54:21.301 --> 54:23.564
What do you think if we just
leave right now?

54:23.608 --> 54:24.739
I don't wanna wait
'til tomorrow.

54:24.783 --> 54:27.133
I thought you wanted
to wait.

54:27.176 --> 54:28.743
- [laughs]
- Let's go. It's two
and a half hours tops.

54:28.787 --> 54:29.875
- So you ready?
- I'm ready.

54:29.918 --> 54:31.137
No, I mean,
you know...

54:31.180 --> 54:32.834
- I'll go change first.
- Okay.

54:35.924 --> 54:37.883
[Bernice humming]

54:40.015 --> 54:41.669
Oh, my goodness!

54:46.152 --> 54:47.458
[crickets chirping]

54:48.807 --> 54:50.896
- [gas can rattles]
- [hacking and spitting]

54:53.681 --> 54:56.205
♪♪

55:14.223 --> 55:15.399
[exhales sharply]

55:15.442 --> 55:17.444
What are you
gonna do to us?

55:17.488 --> 55:20.229
- [groans]
- Billy.

55:20.273 --> 55:23.407
- I don't know.- [Lisa] You guys could just...

55:23.450 --> 55:24.973
let us go,
you can leave.

55:25.017 --> 55:27.759
I mean, there's no need
for anyone else to get hurt.

55:27.802 --> 55:29.326
We won't tell anyone.

55:31.066 --> 55:33.112
This whole night could be
our little secret.

55:33.155 --> 55:36.811
Shh. Stop. Stop.

55:36.855 --> 55:39.118
[Lenny] Something's wrong
with Billy, he's not
right in the head.

55:39.161 --> 55:41.686
Yeah, no kidding.

55:41.729 --> 55:45.037
And that's why he's gonna be
the one to light the match.

55:47.213 --> 55:49.389
What's the matter?
Your arms getting weak?

55:49.433 --> 55:50.738
Yeah.

55:57.832 --> 56:00.922
Here. Make sure
you make the most of it.

56:02.402 --> 56:04.491
Go sit down. Sit.

56:06.667 --> 56:08.582
[Billy] You guys
are not doing this.

56:08.626 --> 56:11.411
- Told you he ain't with us.
- Huh.

56:11.455 --> 56:12.630
There's another way,
all right?

56:12.673 --> 56:14.196
- Move! Move!
- Lenny, come on.

56:14.240 --> 56:15.720
[Juliet] No, no, no, please!

56:15.763 --> 56:17.765
- Please, don't do this.
- Please stop! Stop!

56:18.940 --> 56:21.378
What's the matter
with you?

56:22.640 --> 56:24.685
Come on.

56:24.729 --> 56:25.991
Spit it out.

56:27.471 --> 56:29.342
What do you want me to say?

56:29.386 --> 56:33.259
Oh, is this when you givea shit about some broad?

56:33.302 --> 56:35.217
Well, she's different.

56:36.218 --> 56:37.872
She thinks I'm different.

56:37.916 --> 56:39.178
Mm-hmm.

56:41.049 --> 56:42.747
She just don't
know you yet.

56:43.835 --> 56:45.489
[growling]

56:45.532 --> 56:46.751
[girls screaming]

56:46.794 --> 56:48.709
[Juliet] Oh, my God!

56:48.753 --> 56:50.755
[snarling]

56:50.798 --> 56:53.366
♪♪

56:57.805 --> 57:01.200
- It's Daryl.
- What's left of him.

57:02.723 --> 57:05.030
You two, come on.

57:12.298 --> 57:13.299
[sheriff] All right.

57:15.388 --> 57:18.347
- It's fucking with us.
- What's fucking with us?

57:18.391 --> 57:21.525
Probably whatever
that thing is
killed Daryl.

57:21.568 --> 57:22.917
No, we need to get
the fuck out of here.

57:24.179 --> 57:25.833
Now he's usually
the stupid one,

57:25.877 --> 57:29.968
but you're coming up
close second there, boy.

57:30.011 --> 57:33.188
[inhales sharply]We're gonna hole up here.

57:33.232 --> 57:35.756
Okay? At leastuntil the sun comes up,

57:35.800 --> 57:37.845
and then maybewe might have a shot.

57:37.889 --> 57:40.544
Are you serious? I just poured
fucking gasoline over
everything!

57:40.587 --> 57:43.155
Okay. Got a better idea?

57:45.462 --> 57:48.029
Yeah, I got a better idea.
Give me your gun.
I'll fucking shoot the thing.

57:48.073 --> 57:49.596
That's your plan?
You're gonna fucking
shoot the thing.

57:49.640 --> 57:51.337
You're a fucking idiot.
You know that?

57:51.380 --> 57:53.034
- [Lenny] You shut the fuck up!- Billy.

57:53.078 --> 57:55.994
I want you to find something
to barricade this door.

57:56.037 --> 57:58.344
- Okay?
Like a dining room table.
- This is ridiculous.

57:58.387 --> 58:00.389
We need to lock
this place down.

58:00.433 --> 58:01.913
- Shit! Guys,
we have a problem!
- What?

58:01.956 --> 58:03.305
[Lenny] The girls
are gone.

58:03.349 --> 58:05.438
- [glass shattering]
- It got inside!

58:07.571 --> 58:10.922
No. That's the girls.

58:10.965 --> 58:13.446
They're smashing
all the lightbulbs.

58:13.490 --> 58:15.404
[shattering continues]

58:15.448 --> 58:17.537
All right, hurry up.Find anything you can

58:17.581 --> 58:20.061
and barricade the windows
and barricade all the doors.

58:20.105 --> 58:22.977
Okay? And do itquickly.

58:24.501 --> 58:27.242
[sighs] I'll take care
of the girls.

58:28.592 --> 58:31.333
♪♪

58:31.377 --> 58:33.814
Why are we wastingour time jumpingthrough all of these hoops?

58:33.858 --> 58:35.250
Just follow me.

58:38.558 --> 58:41.343
[grunting] Look, are you
sure this will keep
that fucking thing out?

58:41.387 --> 58:43.389
I say we just cutour fuckin' losses,all right?

58:43.432 --> 58:45.565
Billy, I know
what you're saying.

58:45.609 --> 58:47.306
All right, and?

58:48.742 --> 58:51.005
This is so stupid!Why are we--

58:51.049 --> 58:52.529
- Shh!
- [footsteps on stairs]

58:56.315 --> 58:58.622
[footsteps approaching]

59:01.059 --> 59:03.540
♪♪

01:00:03.295 --> 01:00:06.603
Okay. Unless you have
a better idea, this is
what we're doing.

01:00:06.646 --> 01:00:08.648
[growling]

01:00:09.867 --> 01:00:11.433
Holy shit!

01:00:11.477 --> 01:00:13.044
- [growling]
- [yelling] Dad!

01:00:13.087 --> 01:00:15.612
♪♪

01:00:24.229 --> 01:00:25.578
Get out of the way!

01:00:25.622 --> 01:00:27.014
[snarling, growling]

01:00:29.626 --> 01:00:33.238
- You son of a bitch!
- You got it?

01:00:34.935 --> 01:00:37.198
- It's fucking
with us.
- [Billy] Shit!

01:00:38.983 --> 01:00:41.072
- [Lenny] Now what?
- [sheriff] Damn it!

01:00:44.249 --> 01:00:47.121
- [locking door]
- Okay, so now what?

01:00:47.165 --> 01:00:49.428
That'll buy us some time,but we can't just keep hiding.

01:00:49.471 --> 01:00:50.734
They will find us,eventually.

01:00:50.777 --> 01:00:53.127
- I know. I have a plan.
- Yeah, so do I.

01:00:53.171 --> 01:00:56.391
And it doesn't involverunning around like a bunchof scared little girls, Juliet.

01:00:56.435 --> 01:00:58.655
Lisa, we still need
to find Wendy,

01:00:58.698 --> 01:01:01.570
so my plan first,
okay? Let's go.

01:01:03.355 --> 01:01:05.749
♪♪

01:01:05.792 --> 01:01:08.708
- [sheriff] All right.
- [Billy] Jesus Christ,
what the hell are you doing?

01:01:08.752 --> 01:01:11.232
We gotta save light.

01:01:11.276 --> 01:01:13.626
I've only got six bullets
left in this gun.

01:01:13.670 --> 01:01:16.194
- [Lenny] Are you fucking
kidding me?
- [sheriff] Yeah.

01:01:16.237 --> 01:01:20.285
I got another gun,but it's in the car.

01:01:20.328 --> 01:01:21.939
[Billy] Well,
that's crazy.

01:01:21.982 --> 01:01:23.723
You said it yourself,
we're safer inside.

01:01:23.767 --> 01:01:26.465
Look, I know what I said,but right now,

01:01:26.508 --> 01:01:30.295
I think we might not beso safe down here, okay?

01:01:30.338 --> 01:01:31.949
Okay, so what
are we gonna do?

01:01:33.777 --> 01:01:34.908
We're gonna go up.

01:01:37.084 --> 01:01:39.478
- [Lisa] What if this
doesn't work?
- [Juliet] It will, trust me.

01:01:39.521 --> 01:01:41.959
[sheriff] Oh-ho!

01:01:42.002 --> 01:01:44.962
All right, girls.
You've had your fun.

01:01:45.005 --> 01:01:47.660
Now, we're going
to turn around

01:01:47.704 --> 01:01:49.444
and we're all
gonna go upstairs.

01:01:49.488 --> 01:01:51.185
Is that understood?

01:01:52.883 --> 01:01:55.146
You've got no play
here, woman.

01:01:55.189 --> 01:01:58.845
Juliet, what are we doing?
Let's just do what he says.

01:01:58.889 --> 01:02:00.978
That's right.I'd listen to your sister.

01:02:01.021 --> 01:02:03.720
She's being the smart one
in this situation.

01:02:03.763 --> 01:02:04.982
Huh?

01:02:05.025 --> 01:02:08.986
Okay? No?
Fine.

01:02:09.029 --> 01:02:10.378
Have it your own way.

01:02:10.422 --> 01:02:12.816
Oh, I plan on it!

01:02:16.907 --> 01:02:19.039
[sheriff]Jesus Christ, bitch!

01:02:19.083 --> 01:02:20.737
Setting the fucking houseon fire?

01:02:20.780 --> 01:02:23.870
Let's get out of here!Go! Move! Move!

01:02:29.397 --> 01:02:31.138
- [Lenny coughing]
- This way, come on!

01:02:31.182 --> 01:02:32.966
[sheriff] All right,
just stay low.

01:02:35.664 --> 01:02:38.145
♪♪

01:02:50.114 --> 01:02:52.638
[all coughing]

01:02:59.297 --> 01:03:00.559
[gurgling]

01:03:02.169 --> 01:03:04.302
- [sheriff] Jesus Christ!
- Lenny!

01:03:04.345 --> 01:03:06.739
What the fuck?!
Come on!

01:03:06.783 --> 01:03:09.176
- [choking sounds]
- Billy, let's get
the fuck out of here!

01:03:14.399 --> 01:03:17.532
[breathing hard]

01:03:17.576 --> 01:03:20.971
- So you never told me.
- Never told you what?

01:03:21.014 --> 01:03:22.842
What it was like out there
in the orchard.

01:03:22.886 --> 01:03:25.105
[chuckles] Yeah, and you never
told me that your plan

01:03:25.149 --> 01:03:28.413
entailed burning
the house down, so...
guess we're even.

01:03:28.456 --> 01:03:30.458
Okay, well, my plan wasn't
to burn the house down.

01:03:30.502 --> 01:03:32.504
I just had no options.

01:03:32.547 --> 01:03:35.115
Look, I wanted
to have some fun.

01:03:35.159 --> 01:03:38.815
I wanted my--
our first time
to be special.

01:03:38.858 --> 01:03:41.165
I know you did.

01:03:41.208 --> 01:03:44.255
No apologies necessary.

01:03:44.298 --> 01:03:46.387
- Was it really that good?
- [Lisa chuckles]

01:03:47.824 --> 01:03:50.087
Well, now you're just
holding out on me.

01:03:50.130 --> 01:03:52.785
Okay, I guess
we gotta find Wendy.

01:03:52.829 --> 01:03:54.961
- You'll tell me later.
Let's go.
- [chuckles]

01:04:04.710 --> 01:04:07.191
♪♪

01:04:19.420 --> 01:04:21.945
Jesus!

01:04:21.988 --> 01:04:24.773
